sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Rider
    participant M as Matching Svc
    participant Geo as Redis GEO
    participant D as Driver (WS)
    participant T as Trip Svc (FSM)
    participant P as Pricing/Payment

    Note over R,P: Ride request -> match -> trip lifecycle
    R->>M: POST /ride {pickup, dropoff}
    M->>P: get surge multiplier for cell
    P-->>M: multiplier
    M->>Geo: GEORADIUS drivers 2km
    Geo-->>M: candidate drivers
    M->>M: score (ETA, rating, completion)
    loop offer to top driver (TTL 10-15s)
        M-)D: WS offer
        alt driver accepts
            D--)M: accept
            M->>T: create trip (REQUESTED -> MATCHED)
            T-->>R: matched {driver, ETA}
        else reject or timeout
            Note over M: pick next candidate
        end
    end
    Note over T: MATCHED -> DRIVER_ENROUTE
    D-)T: arrived at pickup
    Note over T: -> ARRIVED -> ON_TRIP
    D-)T: completed at dropoff
    Note over T: ON_TRIP -> COMPLETED
    T->>P: charge fare (server-computed route)
    P-->>T: payment OK
    T-->>R: receipt + rate prompt
